{{!
    @template   block_courselistuv/courselistuv_admin
    @author     2022 Brayan Sanchez Leon <brayan.sanchez.leon@correounivalle.edu.co>
    @author     2022 Iader E. Garcia Gomez <iadergg@gmail.com>
    @author     2022 Juan Felipe Orozco Escobar <juanfe.ores@gmail.com>

    This template renders the content for admin user in courselistuv block.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * course_categories         Array of course categories
        * category_id           String with course category ID
        * url_to_category       String with course category URL
        * category_name         String with course category name
    * url_to_all_courses        String with the URL to course category management

    Example context for admin user (json):
    {
        "course_categories": [
            {
                category_id: 6
                url_to_category: "https://path/to/moodle/course/index.php?categoryid=6"
                category_name: "Cursos Presenciales"
            },
            {
                category_id: 109
                url_to_category: "https://path/to/moodle/course/index.php?categoryid=109"
                category_name: "Cursos Abiertos"
            }
        ]
        "url_to_all_courses": "https://path/to/moodle/course/index.php",
    }
}}

<ul class="unlist">
    {{#course_categories}}
        <li class="course-category-name">
            <div class="m-1">
                <a href="{{url_to_category}}">
                    <i class="fa fa-sitemap fa-fw" role="img" title="{{#str}} course, block_courselistuv {{/str}}" aria-label="{{#str}} course, block_courselistuv {{/str}}"></i>
                    {{category_name}}
                </a>
            </div>
        </li>
    {{/course_categories}}
    <li class="course-category-name">
        <div class="m-1">
            <a href="{{url_to_all_courses}}">
                <i class="fa fa-sitemap fa-fw" role="img" title="{{#str}} course, block_courselistuv {{/str}}" aria-label="{{#str}} course, block_courselistuv {{/str}}"></i>
                {{#str}} all_courses, block_courselistuv {{/str}}
            </a>
        </div>
    </li>
</ul>
